sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant CW as ClaimWorker
    participant Listener as IWorkNotificationListener
    participant Coord as IWorkCoordinator
    participant DB as Postgres
    participant Channels as Per-category channels

    Note over CW: Loop tick: wait for wake signal
    par Wake sources
        Listener->>CW: OnSignal(Outbox/Inbox/Perspective)
    and
        CW->>CW: PollingFallbackInterval timer (default 30s)
    and
        CW->>CW: RequestImmediatePoll() from local producer
    end

    CW->>Coord: ClaimWorkAsync(req)
    Coord->>DB: SELECT * FROM claim_work($instance, $maxStreams, ...)

    alt Empty queues (idle case)
        DB->>DB: 4 EXISTS LIMIT 1 short-circuit (~1ms)
        DB-->>Coord: 0 rows
    else Work available
        DB->>DB: claim_orphaned_* + claim windows + RETURN QUERY (outbox/inbox/perspective)
        opt Full batch returned
            DB-->>CW: RAISE NOTICE 'whizbang.has_more=true'
            Note over CW: Skip wait on next tick (drain mode)
        end
        DB-->>Coord: WorkBatch rows
    end

    Coord-->>CW: WorkBatch
    alt Has work
        CW->>Channels: Distribute (Outboxâ†’IWorkChannelWriter, Inboxâ†’IInboxChannelWriter, Perspectiveâ†’IPerspectiveChannelWriter)
    end

    CW->>CW: Adaptive backoff (250ms â†’ cap)
    Note over CW: Cap = PollingMaxIntervalMs (listener healthy)<br/>OR shorter cap (listener unhealthy)
